description:
Season: 20
Original Air Date: 11/22/2006

Eric gets Nick to take out the non-compete clause of the contract. Everyone unhappily signs the papers. Brooke surprises Nick by also signing away her shares of the stock to him. She tells him that she wants nothing to do with him. Eric and Ridge are overjoyed by Brooke’s loyalty to them. Brooke tells Ridge that she wants to be with him… forever. Stephanie is furious to learn that Eric gave up the company. Bridget is shocked and scared to find Shane at the hospital, who snuck in as her patient for his head injuries. After working on his head, he sneaks out.
